{
  "stem": "15694.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just came from work, and I-- you know, but nevertheless they listened to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Get-- get in line.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but I couldn't keep it up for long, you know, in case one of the real ones would ask me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I tried to get as far back as I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we were marching again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now what's going to happen this time?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can't do the same trick twice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mustn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now we reached the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We turned right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And further we turned left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I must-- and I mustn't get into the light.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although I wasn't afraid that, whatever I would do, that the guard would recognize the boy he had killed about three weeks earlier.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or thought he had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but just as I stepped into the light and I said, oh, too late.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Somebody shouted, enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a few-- quite a few lines in front of me, they were stopped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one behind.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they dispersed-- all dispersed back to the-- their own barracks in no time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Within a minute, everything was cleared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Ah, I said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Saved.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Back to my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'd lost the-- the-- the sense of time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I didn't know would he still be in the metal workshop, or in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I went past our barracks first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I looked inside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I went-- I must confess, slightly proud like a schoolboy with good reports, telling him that not only had I saved myself fourth in line people, but I got out of position where, you know, I was nearly-- that would-- would have nearly been parted from him.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And you know, telling proud now what I did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Proudly what I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What-- what was his reaction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You want to know?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
